name: MEOW
description: Meow is the cutest tiny cat token on the Sui blockchain, packed with whiskers, wonder, and a whole lot of charm. Small in size but bursting with personality, this playful kitty is ready to explore the blockchain world alongside you. Add Meow to your collection and experience Sui's most endearing and adventurous companion, a token that brings joy, curiosity, and a bit of feline mischief wherever it goes!
